187.name: Real GDP at chained PPPs in 2011 US$ (Penn World Table 9.0 (2016))
187.datasetName: Real GDP at chained PPPs in 2011 US$ - Penn World Table 9.0 (2016)

source.name: Penn World Table 9.0 (2016)
source.additionalInfo:
Expenditure-side real GDP at chained PPPs, to compare relative living standards across countries and over time. It is the ratio of the 'rgdpe' and 'pop' series.

More detailed information about this dataset can be found in the source documentation at: http://www.rug.nl/research/ggdc/data/pwt/v90/what_is_new_in_pwt90.pdf

3592.name: Daily fat supply (FAO (2017))
3592.description: Daily fat supply measured in grams per person per day.

source.name: Daily fat supply- FAO (2017)
source.dataPublishedBy: United Nations Food and Agricultural Organization (FAO)
source.additionalInfo:
Daily fat supply is defined as the average per capita fat availability. Note that this indicates the fat availability delivered to households but does not necessarily indicate the quantity of fat actually consumed (food may be wasted at the consumer level).

Data from 1961-1991 for Post-Soviet states are assumed to be in line with reported data for the USSR over this period.
